    • getPageSize

      int getPageSize()
      Returns:
      The number of elements in this page.

    • hasNextPage

      boolean hasNextPage()
      Returns:
      True if there are more pages that can be retrieved from the API.

    • getNextPageToken

      Optional<String> getNextPageToken()
      Returns:
      An Optional of the token string to get the next page. Empty if there is no next page.

    • getNextPage

      Page<E> getNextPage()
      Returns:
      Retrieves the next Page object using the next page token, or returns an empty page if there are no more pages.

    • getItems

      Iterable<E> getItems()
      Returns:
      A List of the elements in this Page.
